➜内蒙古蔬菜价格三个月累计上涨27.36%
http://www.sohu.com/a/434399514_114731	9381
<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201126/4c301ed57e9a4c4781b5040ea3135c24.jpeg" /></p>
